Part A. User Instructions
=========================

  bnfcheck - A universal syntax validation utility.
    See man bnfcheck(1).

A.1. Build instructions
----------------------------

The following software need to be installed
 - pcrecpp library (http://www.pcre.org)

Configure and build the library by executing

autoconf
./configure --prefix=/usr/local
gmake
gmake install

Assuming the software was installed with the /usr/local prefix,
the following environment variables have to be set
  PATH=... :/usr/local/bin
  LD_LIBRARY=... :/usr/local/lib
  MANPATH=... :/usr/local/share/man


